<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.7">
<l>ariyē ṟēye ṉampoṟ cuṭarē ceṅkaṭ karumukilē</l>
<l>yeriyē pavaḷak kuṉṟē nāṟṟō ḷentā yuṉataruḷē</l>
<l>piriyā vaṭimai yeṉṉaik koṇṭāy kuṭantait tirumālē</l>
<l>tariyē ṉiṉiyuṉ caraṇan tanteṉ caṉmaṅ kaḷaiyāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O bull among lions, my golden glow, red-eyed dark cloud,</l>
<l>flame, coral hill, our four-armed father, in your grace</l>
<l>you have taken me into inseparable servantship, Tirumāl in Kuṭantai.</l>
<l>I won’t stop now: give [me] your protection [and] remove my birth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
